// operatorkit.Run. Blocks until ctx cancels — the caller (serverkit)
// runs it in a goroutine.
//
// healthProbeAddr is forwarded from serverkit.Config.OperatorHealthProbeAddr;
// when non-empty operatorkit binds a /healthz + /readyz listener on that
// address for the controller-runtime manager. Empty leaves the manager
// without a probe listener (the default — vanilla forge projects don't
// bind one).
