// Bootstrap constructs all packages and services and registers every
// service on the mux.
//
// NOTE (FORGE_SHAPE_REDESIGN §2): this appkit-table path is the LEGACY DI
// shape. The live composition site is cmd/server.go over the internal/app
// layer (OpenInfra → Build → PostBuild → Inventory). String-keyed service
// selection has been retired — Bootstrap constructs and mounts every
// registered row; which services a binary serves is the registration table
// (pkg/app/services.go), and per-subcommand mount selection lives in the
// cmd layer over internal/app.Inventory.
